Summary: Reported to cause Omenn syndrome in a recessive manner, causing severe immunodeficiency. This effect is recorded in ClinVar by OMIM (http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/clinvar/RCV000014014/) and comes from a case study by Gomez et al 2000 (PMID: 10891502). Gomez et al observed this variant compound heterozygous with another missense variant in a patient.
